{"tid":1495484,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"又一個獌狗示威者 坐監","createTime":"2019-08-22T05:40:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T07:05:14.000Z","uid":54373,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"70581ff71601c56843189fef071aba4f893a2bf8","tid":1495484,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190820/photo/bkn-20190820153809362-0820_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190820173853\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190820%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190820153809362-0820_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190820173853&h=bfc385d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告秦鏡鈞(紅衫)被判監4星期。(何量鈞攝)<br />\n<br />\n持雙程證來港的無業內地漢，聲稱因認為美國與近日香港抗議事件有關，遂由內地攜噴漆到香港，並在美國駐港澳總領事館的大閘噴上「中國必勝」字句，惟未完成時已被領事館的保安阻止並報警求助。該內地漢秦鏡鈞今(20日)於東區法院承認一項刑事損壞罪，被裁判官判處監禁4星期。"},{"pid":"85c3c583d44ee45d91f2a146f2386264dc324e6e","tid":1495484,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:41:26.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守，智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>824 機場復活，WE WANT YOU，而家搭車犯法呀?</strong></span></span> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yrRtRqw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyrRtRqw.jpg&h=a938cd9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wTCkHxb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwTCkHxb.jpg&h=73ff0599&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/00prC5w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F00prC5w.jpg&h=ccabd632&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WJckH